text: Ali Manaj (born November 7, 1937) is an Albanian politician. He was Chairman of the Assembly of the Republic of Albania from February 11, 1976 to December 25, 1978. \- Republika e Shqipërisë KUVEND. Tiranë 2005 He was born in Damës, Gjirokastër. ==References== Category:1937 births Category:Living people Category:Chairpersons of the Parliament of Albania
